  <title>Usar o tablet como canhoto</title>

  <p>Some tablets have hardware buttons on one side. The tablet can be rotated
   180 degrees to position these buttons for left-handed people. To switch the
   orientation to left-handed:</p>

<steps>
  <item><p>Clique em seu nome na barra superior e selecione <gui>Configurações</gui>.</p></item>
  <item><p>Abra <gui>Tablet Wacom</gui>.</p>
     <note style="tip"><p>If no tablet is detected, you'll be asked to
      <gui>Please plug in or turn on your Wacom tablet</gui>.</p></note>
  </item>
  <item><p>Alterne a <gui>Orientação para canhoto</gui> para <gui>LIGADO</gui>.</p></item>
</steps>

